'''弗雷德里克·魏特汉'''（[[德語|德語]]：{{lang|de|Fredric Wertham}}，{{bd|1895年|3月20日|1981年|11月18日|CatIdx=Wertham, Fredric}}）是一位有犹太血统<ref>[http://comicscomicsmag.com/2010/04/jews-and-american-comics-from-another-angle.html "Jews and American Comics from Another Angle"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708180926/http://comicscomicsmag.com/2010/04/jews-and-american-comics-from-another-angle.html |date=2011-07-08 }}</ref>的德裔美籍[[精神病学|精神病学家]]，同时也是一位改革作家，积极抗议[[大众传媒|大众传媒]]和[[漫画|漫画]]上据称对儿童成长有害的暴力画面。<ref name=obit>{{cite news |author= |coauthors= |title=Fredric Wertham, 86, Dies. Foe of Violent TV and Comics |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/01/obituaries/fredric-wertham-86-dies-foe-of-violent-tv-and-comics.html |quote=Dr. Fredric Wertham, an internationally known psychiatrist who believed that comic books, movies and television shows that featured crime, violence and horror exerted a damaging influence on many juveniles and young adults, died November 18 at his retirement home in Kempton, Pennsylvania. He was 86 years old. |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=December 1, 1981 |accessdate=2010-03-29 |first=Bayard |last=Webster |archive-date=2021-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211031054800/https://www.nytimes.com/1981/12/01/obituaries/fredric-wertham-86-dies-foe-of-violent-tv-and-comics.html }}</ref>他最广为人知的著作《诱惑无辜》(1954)，直接导致了[[美国国会|美国国会]]对漫画产业的调查以及[[漫画准则管理局|漫画准则管理局]]的创建。他将[[电视|电视]]称为“[[暴力|暴力]]的学校”，并说：“如果我在一条黑暗的小巷里遇到了一个不守规矩的年轻人，我希望他并没有看过《[[我倆沒有明天|我倆沒有明天]]》（一部改编自美国著名鸳鸯大盗[[邦妮和克莱德|邦妮和克莱德]]的真实故事的动作片）。”<ref name=timeobit>{{cite news |author= |coauthors= |title=Death Revealed |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,925122,00.html#ixzz0jYgn3682 |quote=Fredric Wertham, 86, author and psychiatrist who crusaded against violence in comic books, movies and television; on Nov. 18; in Kempton, Pa. Wertham, a Munich-born authority on criminal psychology, argued that violence is a product of cultural influences. |work=[[Time_magazine|Time magazine]] |date=December 14, 1981 |accessdate=2010-03-29 |archive-date=2010-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101015125849/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,925122,00.html#ixzz0jYgn3682 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 个人简介 ==
魏特汉1895年3月20日生于[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]<ref name=obit/><ref name=timeobit/>。他在德国和英国学习医学，之后与[[西格蒙德·弗洛伊德|弗洛伊德]]一样，选择了[[精神病学|精神病学]]为专业。1922年，他受邀到美国[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]的[[约翰斯·霍普金斯医院|约翰斯·霍普金斯医院]]加入精神病门诊部。他于1927年加入美国籍。<ref name=obit/>1932年，他移居纽约，指导与[[纽约|纽约]]地方刑事法庭相关的一家精神病诊所，对被定罪的犯人进行精神病测试。<ref name=obit/>1935年，魏特汉在[[亚伯特·费雪|亚伯特·费雪]]的审判中作出对他有利的证词，宣称费雪是一名精神病患者。<ref>{{cite news |author= |coauthors= |title=Fish Held Insane By Three Experts. Defense Alienists Say Budd Girl's Murderer Was And Is Mentally Irresponsible |url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F70817FF355B107A93C3AB1788D85F418385F9 |quote=Three psychiatrists testified in Supreme Court today that Albert H. Fish, on trial for the murder of Grace Budd in June, 1928, was legally insane when he committed the murder and has been insane since that date. |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |date=May 21, 1935 |accessdate=2010-03-29 |archive-date=2013-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131127111715/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F70817FF355B107A93C3AB1788D85F418385F9 }}</ref>

== 遗产 ==
他的论文（包括未出版著作《儿童战争》(''The War on Children'')的手稿）都被赠与美国国会图书馆，放置在手稿专区。2010年5月20日起，这批论文开放给学者用于研究用途。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.michaelbarrier.com/Home%20Page/WhatsNewArchivesJuly08.htm |title="Wertham's Locked Vault" |access-date=2010-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125115456/http://michaelbarrier.com/Home%20Page/WhatsNewArchivesJuly08.htm#werthamslockedvault |archive-date=2010-11-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

